<h2>What is the BAT?</h2>
<ul>
<li>Standardized test offered at <a href="https://talentsearch.bloomberginstitute.com/test_sessions/available">750+ top universities worldwide</a></li>
<li>Open to all undergraduate and graduate students</li>
<li>Used by top employers to find best-fit talent</li>
</ul>
